Do I need to send an email to verify my business?

Yes, to proceed with the verification process and have your account approved, please provide the necessary details by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification. You'll need to include your company's full address, legal entity name, EHID or DUNS number, primary contact person's name, and phone number. Once we receive this information, we'll conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status.
